Interface Future_PG

All Superinterfaces:
LockedPG
All Known Implementing Classes:
ClusterPG.Future, CommunityPG.Future, EntityPG.Future, ItemIdentificationPG.Future, LocationSchedulePG.Future, RelationshipPG.Future, TypeIdentificationPG.Future
public interface Future_PG
extends LockedPG

A Future_PG is an instance which represents a promise of information at some point in the future. Any use of the accessors of a Future_PG will block until the properties are actually available. An LDM plugin may initially supply a Future_PG of the appropriate class rather than a real PG in order to back-fill later.

Method Summary
